Package Server.Collections

Class CollectionManager

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractSet<E>
java.util.HashSet<Vehicle>
Server.Collections.CollectionManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Vehicle>, Collection<Vehicle>, Set<Vehicle>
public class CollectionManager extends HashSet<Vehicle>
This class extends HashSet and is responsible for managing a collection of Vehicle objects. It provides methods for adding, clearing, getting and removing vehicles by their ID, and removing all vehicles by their engine power.
